videos.headline: W. Michigan snatches lead from Northwestern
videos.description: Western Michigan makes a push for a touchdown on fourth down after a failed 2-point conversion, making the score 22-21.

videos.headline: Northwestern fumbles away chance to take lead
videos.description: Northwestern's Clayton Thorson fumbles at the Western Michigan 1-yard line with the play ultimately being called a touchback after review.

videos.description: Western Michigan pulls off a big upset against Northwestern, who won their 2015 season opener against Stanford.

videos.headline: Northwestern QB fumbles at worst possible time
videos.description: Down by one point, Northwestern QB Clayton Thorson fumbles just before crossing the goal line resulting in a touchback.
